      "seed": 914406002,
      "version": 956,
      "versionNonce": 850116065,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782028082563,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Problem:",
      "fontSize": 26.8,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Problem:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "2xn0y2ajhwz_XF5H6ZwMi",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 78.95518092105272,
      "y": 246.8048930921052,
      "width": 924.4615478515625,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 70,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a2",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1469075630,
      "version": 322,
      "versionNonce": 1360746945,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782028082563,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "We learnt that SOLID principles ensure that our code doesn't get tightly-coupled, but it's\nnot a hard rule and we break it sometimes to make code simpler.\nDesign-Patterns are general standard solution to common occuring problems.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "We learnt that SOLID principles ensure that our code doesn't get tightly-coupled, but it's not a hard rule and we break it sometimes to make code simpler.\nDesign-Patterns are general standard solution to common occuring problems.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "1-kKQHJ98E3UpJRmAllas",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 73.13456324527147,
      "y": 385.9884868421052,
      "width": 924.4615478515625,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 70,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a3",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 697949678,
      "version": 673,
      "versionNonce": 86306927,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782028147185,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Similarly we also have Anti-Patterns; basically things which make our code more complex and\nless maintainable. \nAvoiding these Anti-Pattern problems helps in:\n- loose-coupling\n- leverage design-patterns easily\n- easily integrate new code",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Similarly we also have Anti-Patterns; basically things which make our code more complex and less maintainable. \nAvoiding these Anti-Pattern problems helps in:\n- loose-coupling\n- leverage design-patterns easily\n- easily integrate new code",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "pR2IYx2fXiK5dNZgKbeSM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 82.16096496582031,
      "y": 705.55859375,
      "width": 186.36703491210938,
      "height": 33.5,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 80,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a4",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 382129582,
      "version": 975,
      "versionNonce": 944353906,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782021516587,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. God Object:",
      "fontSize": 26.8,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. God Object:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "A7YVH3BCiwusEvnytDiJb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 92.90985107421875,
      "y": 765.56640625,
      "width": 924.4615478515625,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 70,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a5",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 723283570,
      "version": 810,
      "versionNonce": 1330053426,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782024248572,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Single class having so much responsibility to handle. Almost every method goes through this\none class which makes whole system tightly coupled; and this one class behaves as God also\nbecoming single point of failure.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Single class having so much responsibility to handle. Almost every method goes through this one class which makes whole system tightly coupled; and this one class behaves as God also becoming single point of failure.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
