      "updated": 1782027699230,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "9. Inheritance overuse:",
      "fontSize": 26.8,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "9. Inheritance overuse:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "V2CNNBBS4KbcG274_-i30",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 56.483121967409915,
      "y": 5044.1800002194495,
      "width": 863.6778762817383,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "cross-hatch",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 70,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1L",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1830126894,
      "version": 3034,
      "versionNonce": 884216494,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782028006632,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "As we already discussed in past: prefer Composition over Inheritance. Utilizing multiple\n& multi-level inheritance makes code unnecessarily complex and long.\n\nTo avoid this only we came up with Strategy, Visitor & Bridge design-pattern.\nWe in past problems always tried to use only Inheritance through only one Abstract\nclass and in concrete implementations have Composition through 'has-a' relation.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "As we already discussed in past: prefer Composition over Inheritance. Utilizing multiple & multi-level inheritance makes code unnecessarily complex and long.\n\nTo avoid this only we came up with Strategy, Visitor & Bridge design-pattern.\nWe in past problems always tried to use only Inheritance through only one Abstract class and in concrete implementations have Composition through 'has-a' relation.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
  ],
